Package com.tangosol.coherence.rest.config

Class ResourceConfig

java.lang.Object
com.tangosol.coherence.rest.config.ResourceConfig
public class ResourceConfig extends Object
The ResourceConfig class encapsulates information related to a Coherence REST resource.
